<h1 id=3D"id-06-IMSInformationSecurityCommunicationPlan-Effectivenessandade=
quacyofthedocument">Effectiveness and adequacy of the document</h1>
<p>When evaluating the effectiveness and adequacy of this document, the fol=
lowing criteria need to be considered:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>number of incidents related to a missing, incorrect or delayed communica=
tion,</p></li>
<li>
<p>number of use cases not addressed by this policy.</p></li>
</ul>
